snippet: Chicago police said on Wednesday they charged a Minnesota man in the 2009 rape and murder of a 12-year-old Chicago girl on the basis of DNA evidence from another rape case....

headline.print_headline: Minnesota Man Charged in 2009 Murder of 12-Year-Old Chicago Girl
headline.main: Minnesota Man Charged in 2009 Murder of 12-Year-Old Chicago Girl

lead_paragraph: Chicago police said on Wednesday they charged a Minnesota man in the 2009 rape and murder of a 12-year-old Chicago girl on the basis of DNA evidence from another rape case.
